<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA87">
<l>nāmālai cūṭiyu nammīcaṉ poṉṉaṭikkē</l>
<l>pūmālai koṇṭu puṉaintaṉpāy - nāmō</l>
<l>raṟiviṉaiyē paṟṟiṉā leṟṟē taṭumē</l>
<l>yeṟiviṉaiyē yeṉṉu miruḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When we put on a tongue garland, decorate, taking</l>
<l>a flower garland to the golden feet of our lord, lovingly,</l>
<l>[and] hold on to one knowledge, how, which can the</l>
<l>darkness called attacking karma kill?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
